---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="MSRM is one platform to run restaurants end-to-end, built for Australia.">
  <section class="container-x py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="h1 text-4xl sm:text-5xl mt-3">One platform, the whole restaurant.</h1>
    <p class="lead mt-5">Restaurants were stitching together a POS, a kitchen screen, a stock sheet, aggregator dashboards and an accountant — none of them talking to each other. MSRM brings it all into one real-time system, built from day one for <strong>Australian restaurants</strong>.</p>
    <p class="lead mt-4">From a single café to a multi-outlet chain, MSRM runs the floor, the kitchen, the back office and the books — so owners spend less time reconciling and more time serving.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="card text-center"><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-600">Unified</div><p class="text-sm text-ink-mute mt-1">12+ modules, one login</p></div>
      <div class="card text-center"><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-600">Real-time</div><p class="text-sm text-ink-mute mt-1">Sale → stock → books instantly</p></div>
      <div class="card text-center"><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-600">Local</div><p class="text-sm text-ink-mute mt-1">GST/BAS, local payments</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTA />
</Layout>
